{"tid":2294278,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"薛永恒：對強制市民下載行蹤程式持開放及大膽態度 認為強制店舖參與是合理","createTime":"2020-11-21T01:59:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-21T02:27:51.000Z","uid":21470,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"bc76d70c77bc8e0620ef89e3c02a6a52958c8541","tid":2294278,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T01:59:24.000Z","msg":"薛永恒：市民對安心出行應用程式反應積極<br />\n<br />\n創新及科技局局長薛永恒在一個電台節目表示，自「安心出行」應用程式推出以來，至今有超過1.2萬個公私營處所參與，當中5000個屬私營處所，形容市民反應非常積極，程式的認受性高。被問到會否強制市民下載，薛永恒指，本港疫情越來越嚴峻，對如何使用好手上的工具抗疫，應持開放及大膽態度，不排除任何可能性，若有需要強制以用好抗疫科技，有市民支持就會做。<br />\n<br />\n他指，若在防疫抗疫角度考慮，強制店舖參與「安心出行」亦是合理，若要強制使用，資源會相對集中在高風險場所，例如考慮在特定處所現時的防疫要求下，加入必須參與「安心出行」的條款等。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2367251\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2367251&d=HaoFMq3H8OfxnxI562yM34bsTeectjBlsojPGUwt5kI%3D&h=d81e7020\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2367251</a>"},{"pid":"78f0dd70331e4970a8f26f41fbd56860d81579b1","tid":2294278,"uid":290118,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T02:09:31.000Z","msg":"安心上路<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2eebf96cdd8f5ba880221b6fbba85e1888fcf684","tid":2294278,"uid":59931,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T02:14:22.000Z","msg":"邊間做咪唔去邊間<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef293a640ac03f81bedd3aafe08e50693d80b648","tid":2294278,"uid":366932,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T02:27:51.000Z","msg":"露底了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n前兩日先話唔會強制，比班保皇黨講兩句就轉哂呔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}